<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1209540-i-love-history-but-these-princes-n">I love history....but these princes n princesses or yore have so many names...I am confused at times...Salim and Jahangir?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1209540'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F27298.The_Twentieth_Wife">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1209540-i-love-history-but-these-princes-n">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1209540-i-love-history-but-these-princes-n">Add your answer</a>
