              <span id="reviewTextContainer2174097312" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15348761763860647418">Took me awhile to get into this book but now ready for the 2nd in the trilogy. Enjoyed candid ‘conversation’ with the author and insight concerning historical research versus re-creating India 400 years ago.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


